      "content": "That's what the field reports say, but the satellite imagery we just intercepted shows heavy artillery being moved into the forward positions, not just security personnel. That looks a lot more than \"routine logistics\" to me. Are you certain you aren't downplaying the severity here? I need to know if your assessment accounts for the specific hardware being deployed.",
